summary: Glory from Alliance Insurance followed up on an endorsement request for JJJ Commercial and Residential Cleaning LLC, leaving a voicemail for Ali at AutoOwnersInsurance to process the request and issue a COI. The call resulted in a voicemail since Ali was unavailable.
